### Create a team
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teams
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Team India",
  "country": "India"
}

###
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teams
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Australia",
  "country": "Australia"
}

### Get all teams
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teams

### Get team by id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teams/1

### Create players assigned to a team
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/players
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Virat Kohli",
  "matches": 500,
  "runs": 12000,
  "average": 65.67,
  "teamId": 1
}

###
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/players
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Rohit Sharma",
  "matches": 450,
  "runs": 10000,
  "average": 55.50,
  "teamId": 1
}

###
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/players
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Steve Smith",
  "matches": 400,
  "runs": 9000,
  "average": 60.00,
  "teamId": 2
}

### Create player without a team (teamId optional)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/players
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "MS Dhoni",
  "matches": 350,
  "runs": 8000,
  "average": 50.00
}

### Update team name
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teams/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Team India",
  "country": "India"
}

### Get all players
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/players

### Get player by id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/players/1

### Update player
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/players/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Virat Kohli",
  "matches": 510,
  "runs": 12500,
  "average": 66.00,
  "teamId": 1
}

### Delete player
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/players/2

### Test validation - should return 400
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/players
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "matches": -5,
  "runs": -100,
  "average": -1.0
}

### Test not found - should return 404
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/players/999